 5	## Environment Setup
 6	
 7	### Create Environment File
 8	Before starting, create a `.env` file in the `backend` folder:
 9	
 10	1. Copy the example file:
 11	```bash
 12	cd backend
 13	cp .env.example .env
 14	```
 15	
 16	2. Edit the `.env` file and add your private key:
 17	```env
 18	# Required: Private key for contract deployment (without 0x prefix)
 19	PRIVATE_KEY=your_private_key_here_without_0x_prefix
 20	
 21	# Optional: RPC URLs for testnets (only needed for testnet deployment)
 22	FTM_RPC_URL=https://rpc.blaze.soniclabs.com
 23	SEPOLIA_RPC_URL=https://sepolia.infura.io/v3/YOUR_PROJECT_ID
 24	```
 25	
 26	** Important**:
 27	- Remove the `0x` prefix from your private key
 28	- For local development, you can use any test private key
 29	- **To export from MetaMask**: Go to Account Details Export Private Key
 30	- Never use real funds or mainnet private keys
