 32	## Quick Start Guide
 33	
 34	### Prerequisites
 35	
 36	Before you begin, make sure you have these installed on your computer:
 37	
 38	1. **Node.js** (version 16 or higher)
 39	 - Download from: https://nodejs.org/
 40	 - Choose the LTS version
 41	
 42	2. **npm** or **yarn** (comes with Node.js)
 43	 - npm is included with Node.js
 44	 - For yarn: `npm install -g yarn`
 45	
 46	3. **MetaMask Browser Extension**
 47	 - Install from: https://metamask.io/
 48	 - Create a wallet if you don't have one
 49	
 50	4. **Git** (to clone the repository)
 51	 - Download from: https://git-scm.com/
