 55	## Installation
 56	
 57	### Step 1: Clone the Repository
 58	```bash
 59	git clone https://github.com/DescLending-Project/blockchain-prototyping-sose2025.git
 60	cd "blockchain-prototyping-sose2025/Lending (BC) + frontend/loan-management"
 61	```
 62	
 63	### Step 2: Install Dependencies
 64	```bash
 65	# Install root dependencies
 66	npm install
 67	
 68	# Install backend dependencies
 69	cd backend
 70	npm install
 71	
 72	# Install frontend dependencies
 73	cd ../frontend
 74	npm install
 75	
 76	# Go back to root directory
 77	cd ..
 78	```
