 218	## Advanced Features
 219	
 220	### Zero-Knowledge Proofs (ZK)
 221	The platform includes experimental ZK proof functionality for enhanced privacy:
 222	
 223	```bash
 224	cd backend
 225	npx hardhat run scripts/deployAll-ZK.js --network localhost
 226	```
 227	
 228	This deploys additional contracts for:
 229	- Private credit scoring
 230	- Confidential transaction verification
 231	- Advanced privacy features
 232	
 233	### Automated Mockup Simulation
 234	The `run-mockup-after-deploy.js` script creates realistic platform activity:
 235	
 236	- **Lender Simulation**: 2 months of lending activity with deposits, withdrawals, and interest claims
 237	- **Borrower Simulation**: Multiple borrow/repay cycles with collateral management
 238	- **Credit Score Updates**: Dynamic credit scoring based on behavior
 239	
 240	This runs automatically after deployment but can be triggered manually:
 241	```bash
 242	cd backend
 243	npx hardhat run scripts/run-mockup-after-deploy.js --network localhost
 244	```
 245	
 246	---
 247	
 248	## Troubleshooting
 249	
 250	### Common Issues
 251	
 252	#### "Connect Wallet" Button Not Working
 253	- Make sure MetaMask is installed and unlocked
 254	- Verify you're on the "Localhost 8545" network
 255	- Check that the Hardhat node is running
 256	
 257	#### MetaMask Loads But Won't Connect
 258	If MetaMask opens but doesn't connect to the application:
 259	- **Open MetaMask in a separate tab**: Click the MetaMask extension icon and select "Expand view" to open it in a full browser tab
 260	- **Keep MetaMask tab open**: Leave the expanded MetaMask tab open while using the application
 261	- **Log in manually**: Make sure you're logged into MetaMask in the expanded tab
 262	- **Try connecting again**: Return to the application and click "Connect Wallet"
 263	
 264	> ** Tip**: Sometimes MetaMask needs to be opened and logged into separately before it can connect to web applications. Opening it in an expanded view helps establish a stable connection.
 265	
 266	#### "Transaction Failed" Errors
 267	- Ensure you have enough ETH for gas fees
 268	- Try refreshing the page
 269	- Switch to a different account if needed
 270	
 271	#### "Contract Not Found" Errors
 272	- Make sure contracts are deployed: `npx hardhat run scripts/deployAll.js --network localhost`
 273	- Restart the Hardhat node if needed
 274	- Clear browser cache and refresh
 275	
 276	### Reset Everything
 277	If something goes wrong, restart from scratch:
 278	
 279	1. Stop all running processes (Ctrl+C in terminals)
 280	2. Restart Hardhat node: `cd backend && npx hardhat node`
 281	3. Redeploy contracts: `npx hardhat run scripts/deployAll.js --network localhost`
 282	4. Restart frontend: `npm run dev`
 283	
 284	---
 285	
 286	## Project Structure
 287	
 288	```
 289	loan-management/
 290	 backend/ # Smart contracts and blockchain logic
 291	 contracts/ # Solidity smart contracts
 292	 scripts/ # Deployment and utility scripts
 293	 test/ # Contract tests
 294	 .env # Environment variables (create this)
 295	 hardhat.config.js # Blockchain configuration
 296	 frontend/ # React web application
 297	 src/ # Frontend source code
 298	 package.json # Frontend dependencies
 299	 README.md # This file
 300	```
