 127	## Notes
 128	
 129	- The artifacts are copied as-is, preserving the full structure including ABI, bytecode, and metadata
 130	- The script will overwrite existing files in the frontend
 131	- If a contract artifact is missing, the script will report an error and exit
 132	- The script creates the frontend directory if it doesn't exist
 133	- Address updates are network-aware and will use the correct stablecoin addresses for each network
 134	- The CORAL token address remains unchanged as it's a fixed address ...
