 164	
 165	## Using the Platform
 166	
 167	### Step 1: Connect Your Wallet
 168	1. Visit **http://localhost:5173**
 169	2. Click "Connect Wallet"
 170	3. Select MetaMask
 171	4. Choose one of your imported accounts
 172	5. Make sure you're on the "Localhost 8545" network
 173	
 174	### Step 2: Explore Different Roles
 175	
 176	#### As a Lender 
 177	- Switch to a lender account in MetaMask
 178	- Deposit ETH into the liquidity pool
 179	- Earn interest on your deposits
 180	- Withdraw funds when needed
 181	
 182	#### As a Borrower 
 183	- Switch to a borrower account in MetaMask
 184	- Deposit collateral (GLINT tokens)
 185	- Borrow ETH against your collateral
 186	- Repay loans to maintain healthy positions
 187	
