 205	### Generate Mock Transactions
 206	To populate the frontend with realistic data:
 207	```bash
 208	cd backend
 209	npx hardhat run scripts/mockTransactions.js --network localhost
 210	```
 211	
 212	This creates sample transactions for testing the user interface.
